  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户和系统之间的交互流程，核心场景是：用户发消息，然后系统要通知用户有人对他的消息做了反应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "System",
        "message",
        "reaction",
        "notify"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，是两个参与者对吧？User作为触发方，System作为处理方。我想确认一下——通知的内容是\"别人对你的消息有反应\"，还是系统自己产生的反应？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "System",
        "notify",
        "reaction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是别人产生的反应，System只是负责把这个通知推送给原消息的作者。所以箭头应该是从System指向User，表示系统主动通知。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "System",
        "User",
        "Notify about reaction on own message"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出框架：User发送消息给System，然后System回送一个通知。第一笔交互我标注为\"Send message\"，第二笔是\"Notify about reaction on own message\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User-System",
        "System-User",
        "Send message",
        "Notify about reaction on own message"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，\"Notify about reaction on own message\"这个表述会不会太长？不过意思是对的——强调是\"自己的消息\"被反应了。先这样吧，保持语义清晰更重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Notify about reaction on own message"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下整体结构：参与者是User和System，User是actor类型，System是普通participant。交互顺序是User先发，System后通知。没有遗漏的分支吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "actor User",
        "participant System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没遗漏，这个场景就是简单的两步：发消息触发了后续的通知机制。User和System的关系就是这样，不需要再拆成更多步骤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "System",
        "Send message",
        "Notify about reaction on own message"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。User作为actor发起Send message到System，System再反向Notify about reaction on own message给User，整个通知闭环画好了。",
